column5: Hey Guys, just finished up my latest ice fishing video.  This is the 3rd year I've made a video with footage from the previous winter.  Definitely gets me in the mood to hit the ice.  Check it outâ€¦ hope you like it!  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wsaiv5_pSkU  Don't forget to select 1080HD  Thanks for watching!
Great stuff Ben... but you put the wrong year on it!
Awesome as usual Ben !!!! Wow.... Some big fish man ..tight-lines and keep those vids Comming
Great video, great tune ! ... I'm guessing it should be 2013 ... You guys up north there get all the fun !!!
great job on the video, gotta love those Lake trout
That's a great video Ben!  Hope this season is just as good or better as the last!
Always a guy to keep an eye on.  Whole-heartedly loves the outdoors and the life.  Be sure you keep the gang here in the loop through the winter and paste those RB's reports this way.
Yeah buddy!!! That got me all fired up!!  S.
Well done!  Some great fish there and awesome editing.  Burt
Great vid! Can't wait to hit some ice.
Thanks guys.  And no, I meant 2014!!  This video is for the coming ice season, the 2013 ice season was last year.
Great vid and choice in music!
